MTQ_Items_1-12_1: MTQ_Items_1-12 - 1. When I become interested in something, I try to learn as much about it as I can.

MTQ_Items_1-12_3: MTQ_Items_1-12 - 3. It really upsets me when someone does something better than I do.

MTQ_Items_1-12_8: MTQ_Items_1-12 - 8. If I already do something well, I don't see the need to challenge myself to do better.
